body.description: Graco Extend2Fit 3-in-1 Car Seat, StocklynThe Graco Extend2Fit 3-in-1 Car Seat features a 4-position extension panel that provides up to 5” of extra rear-facing legroom, allowing your child to ride safely rear-facing longer. Children are safer riding rear-facing and should ride rear-facing as long as possible, until they reach the maximum rear-facing height or weight rating for their car seat. The adjustable extension panel and 50 lb rear-facing weight limit allow the seat to grow with your child in rear-facing mode, providing extended rear-facing use. This seat offers 3 modes of use to grow with your child from rear-facing harness (4-50 lb) to forward-facing harness (22-65 lb) to highback booster (40-100 lb). The seat features the Simply Safe Adjust Harness System, which allows you to adjust the height of the harness and headrest in one motion, and InRight LATCH for a one-second LATCH attachment. Harnessing is made easier with fuss-free harness storage pockets that conveniently hold the harness out of the way while getting baby in and out of the car seat.Graco Tranzitions 3 in 1 Harness Booster Seat, ProofGraco Transitions 3-in-1 harness booster car seat is designed to grow with your child and go with you, wherever your journeys take you - from car to carpool and beyond. This lightweight car seat transitions seamlessly from harness booster (22 - 65 lbs) to highback booster (40 - 100 lbs) to backless booster seat (40 - 100 lbs) and features the Simply Safe Adjust Harness System, which adjusts your harness and headrest to 8 height positions, with no rethreading. It features two removable cup holders to keep your child happy, and a machine washable seat pad, body insert and harness covers. Metal and plastic parts may be cleaned with mild soap and cool water.
